{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782402318233,"sessionID":"ses_1008b4e19ffekRdAT5Lxgyqh5H","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_lyxjXBXvFs6gdJQCmH2vmOVD","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-task-checklist.md","limit":260},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-task-checklist.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Phase Task Checklist\n2: \n3: - Phase: `phase-04-home-history-discovery`\n4: \n5: ## Purpose\n6: \n7: Current-phase task checklist generated from the agent-maintained source coverage matrix and platform capability check. Use it before editing and update the matrix/check after work.\n8: \n9: ## Summary\n10: \n11: | metric | value |\n12: | --- | --- |\n13: | phaseFeatureEntries | 30 |\n14: | phaseCriticalHighFeatureEntries | 26 |\n15: | mustCompleteFeatureEntries | 26 |\n16: | needsEvidenceFeatureEntries | 0 |\n17: | deferredOrFallbackFeatureEntries | 0 |\n18: | coveredFeatureEntries | 0 |\n19: | phaseSourceFiles | 9 |\n20: | phasePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n21: | phaseCriticalHighPlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n22: | mustCompletePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n23: | needsEvidencePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n24: | implementationGroups | 4 |\n25: | planContractAvailable | True |\n26: | planContractMatchedGroups | 2 |\n27: | planContractUnmatchedGroups | 0 |\n28: | implementationGroupSourceBehavior | 3 |\n29: | implementationGroupResourceMigration | 0 |\n30: | implementationGroupPlatformCapability | 0 |\n31: | implementationGroupVerification | 1 |\n32: | implementationGroupArchitectureRisk | 0 |\n33: | implementationGroupUiContracts | 1 |\n34: | behaviorAuditFeatureContracts | 26 |\n35: | behaviorAuditOpenFeatureContracts | 0 |\n36: | behaviorAuditPlatformContracts | 0 |\n37: | testHarnessReportAvailable | True |\n38: | testHarnessAcceptedPass | False |\n39: | unassignedCriticalHighFeatureEntries | 116 |\n40: | unassignedCriticalHighPlatformCapabilityEntries | 5 |\n41: \n42: ## Feature Status Counts\n43: \n44: | status | count |\n45: | --- | --- |\n46: | planned | 30 |\n47: \n48: ## Plan Contract Alignment\n49: \n50: Use this section as upstream planning ownership evidence. If it conflicts with source code, source-coverage-matrix.json, or platform-capability-check.json, resolve the authority records or document an analysis gap/source override before closing the phase.\n51: \n52: ### Matched Plan Groups\n53: \n54: | group id | type | priority | matched generated groups | source paths | features | capabilities | risks |\n55: | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n56: | phase-04-home-content | source-behavior | critical | phase-04-home-history-discovery-source-behavior-presentation-components, phase-04-home-history-discovery-source-behavior-presentation-home, phase-04-home-history-discovery-verification-phase-tests-and-evidence | app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/home/HomeScreen.kt, app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/home/HomeViewModel.kt, app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/home/components |  | localization-resources | Do not push home-specific state into the global shell.; Search and filter controls are visible behavior even without backend filtering. |\n57: | phase-04-history-tabs | ui-contract | high | phase-04-home-history-discovery-source-behavior-presentation-history, phase-04-home-history-discovery-verification-phase-tests-and-evidence | app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/history/History.kt, app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/history/HistoryViewModel.kt, app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/history/components/Tabs.kt |  | localization-resources | The source history section is largely placeholder content; keep visible structure without inventing backend behavior. |\n58: \n59: ## Behavior Audit\n60: \n61: | metric | value |\n62: | --- | --- |\n63: | featureContracts | 26 |\n64: | openFeatureCon